{
  "info": {
    "name": "NerdQuiz API",
    "description": "Complete API collection for NerdQuiz — ITPEC FE exam prep platform.\n\n## Setup\n1. Set `base_url` to your backend URL (e.g. `https://your-api.onrender.com`)\n2. Set `jwt_token` to a valid Supabase JWT bearer token\n3. Public endpoints (Health, Exam Sessions) work without auth\n\n## Auth\nAll endpoints except Health and Exam Sessions require:\n```\nAuthorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}\n```\n\n## Supabase Cloud\n- **Supabase URL:** Set `supabase_url` variable\n- **Supabase Anon Key:** Set `supabase_anon_key` variable (for direct Supabase calls if needed)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:8080",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "jwt_token",
      "value": "YOUR_SUPABASE_JWT_TOKEN_HERE",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "supabase_url",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "supabase_anon_key",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{jwt_token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Get JWT Token",
      "description": "Get a Supabase JWT token by signing in. Use this first, then copy the token into the `jwt_token` collection variable.\n\n**Steps:**\n1. If you don't have a user yet, run **Sign Up** first\n2. Run **Sign In** with your email + password\n3. Copy the `access_token` from the response\n4. Set it as the `jwt_token` collection variable",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Sign Up (create new user)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.access_token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('jwt_token', res.access_token);",
                  "    console.log('Token saved! Access token: ' + res.access_token.substring(0, 50) + '...');",
                  "} else {",
                  "    console.log('Sign up response: ' + JSON.stringify(res));",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{supabase_url}}/auth/v1/signup",
              "host": ["{{supabase_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "v1", "signup"]
            },
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "apikey",
                "value": "{{supabase_anon_key}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"testuser@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"TestPass123!\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Sign In (get JWT token)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.access_token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('jwt_token', res.access_token);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('user_id', res.user.id);",
                  "    console.log('Token saved!');",
                  "    console.log('User ID: ' + res.user.id);",
                  "    console.log('Access token: ' + res.access_token.substring(0, 50) + '...');",
                  "} else {",
                  "    console.log('Sign in failed: ' + JSON.stringify(res));",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{supabase_url}}/auth/v1/token?grant_type=password",
              "host": ["{{supabase_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "v1", "token"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "grant_type",
                  "value": "password"
                }
              ]
            },
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "apikey",
                "value": "{{supabase_anon_key}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"testuser@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"TestPass123!\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.access_token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('jwt_token', res.access_token);",
                  "    console.log('Token refreshed!');",
                  "} else {",
                  "    console.log('Refresh failed: ' + JSON.stringify(res));",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{supabase_url}}/auth/v1/token?grant_type=refresh_token",
              "host": ["{{supabase_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "v1", "token"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "grant_type",
                  "value": "refresh_token"
                }
              ]
            },
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "apikey",
                "value": "{{supabase_anon_key}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refresh_token\": \"YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Current User (from token)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{supabase_url}}/auth/v1/user",
              "host": ["{{supabase_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "v1", "user"]
            },
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "apikey",
                "value": "{{supabase_anon_key}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}"
              }
            ]
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
